Having Each Other.complete(The L Word interest)

JB&JB is cutting and remaking The L Word Season 1-5 into about 13 parts renamed Having Each Other. In this new edition, Bette, Tina and Jenny are leading actors, and they are the main clues. Others are mostly removed. Having Each Other is a good series teaching us how to love each other and have each other.

Information

The video quality of the new series is the same as the video with 350MB size.
